Question
Given a number N, find the Nth term in the series 1, 3, 6, 10, 15, 21â€¦

Solution:
class Solution
{
  public:
    int findNthterm(int N)
    {
      int i=1;
      if(N==1)
        return 1;
      int p=1;
      while(i<N)
      {
          i++;
          p=p+i;
      }
    }
    return p;
  }

Explaination:
* First initialize i=1
* Iterate i from 1 to n add i to p in each iteration
* Everytime increment i
* Return p
